
Ranger Help for: beach
======================

SUMMARY:    
Beaches are any area where water meets land. It could be the side of a
lake, river of sea. They are usually have similar characteristics no
matter the water source, such as water erosion, marine animals and
plants. The Ranger population on beaches is fairly small, but beaches
can be found on all of the continents. Ranger skills are somewhat
limited on beaches. The only exception is the port, ports join land to
water but are not considered beaches.

=============================================================================
